✨ KEY FEATURES

• Massive anime database — 10,000+ anime series with metadata
• Multiple sources — Nyaa, AniDex, TokyoTosho, and custom trackers
• Smart search — filter by genre, year, season, status, and popularity
• Batch downloads — download entire series with one click
• Quality selection — 480p, 720p, 1080p, and 4K when available
• Subtitle integration — auto-download subtitles in multiple languages
• Library management — organize, track progress, and mark watched
• Resume support — continue downloads after restart
• Speed limits — control bandwidth usage
• Schedule downloads — set time windows for downloading
• Dark mode — easy on the eyes for night browsing
• Portable — runs from USB, no registry changes
• 100% open source — MIT license, contribute on GitHub

