🔧 HOW TO USE

SEARCHING ANIME
────────────────────────────────
1. Type anime name in search bar
2. Use filters to narrow results (genre, year, status)
3. Click on any result to see details
4. View episode list, synopsis, and ratings

DOWNLOADING EPISODES
────────────────────────────────
1. Select episodes you want (or click "Select All")
2. Choose quality preference
3. Click "Download Selected"
4. Monitor progress in Download Manager
5. Find files in your library folder

MANAGING LIBRARY
────────────────────────────────
1. Click "My Library" tab
2. Browse downloaded episodes by series
3. Double-click to play (opens default video player)
4. Right-click for options (delete, mark watched, show in folder)
5. Track watched status and progress

SETTINGS & CUSTOMIZATION
────────────────────────────────
1. Click ⚙ Settings icon
2. Change download location
3. Set speed limits
4. Configure simultaneous downloads
5. Enable/disable auto-updates

